      "content": "I'm looking at two potential areas for a new residential development project. Can you give me a quick risk/stability comparison for these two types of neighborhoods?\n\nArea A: An established, historic district with high socio-economic stability and a consistent, long-term resident base.\n\nArea B: A high-density urban zone experiencing rapidly changing demographics and high population turnover. \n\nWhich one would you classify as the lower-risk investment for long-term property value appreciation?",
